It means that you need to go to your router and open the port of your server which is 43594 (Default) simply do this:

In the port list you must set the port 43594 and protocol TCP, then do the same with the UDP protocol but don’t put the port leave it in 0…

doesn't that mean people can then get into my computer of somthing??
Yes it means people will go to your computer/server, they will only enter to play the server NOT to your computer(Documents and other stuff) :)
